      "content": "hey my left eye is super red and it's kinda hurting a bit... there's also this yellow crusty stuff in it when i wake up. i've been staring at my laptop for like 10 hours a day for work so i think it's just really bad dry eyes. can i just use some regular artificial tears maybe twice a day to fix it?",
