      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's kind of a pain to go to the doctor though, and i have so much work to finish this week. if i use the ointment and maybe some redness relief drops like the ones with vasoconstrictors to take the red out, do you think that'll clear it up by tomorrow? i really don't want to deal with an infection or anything if it's just from the screen time.",
